            <!--CREDITS-->
            <TextBlock Margin="0,10,0,0">
            作者 - <Hyperlink NavigateUri="https://github.com/isHuaMouRen" Click="Hyperlink_Click">isHuaMouRen</Hyperlink><LineBreak/>
            项目储存库 - <Hyperlink NavigateUri="https://github.com/isHuaMouRen/image-hider-based-on-alpha" Click="Hyperlink_Click">在Github上查看</Hyperlink>
